trans-unit.source: Passed to the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IServiceContractGenerationExtension.GenerateContract%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method to enable the modification of a service contract and its context prior to generating code.
trans-unit.target: Przekazany do <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IServiceContractGenerationExtension.GenerateContract%2A?displayProperty=fullName> metody, aby umożliwić modyfikowanie kontrakt usługi i kontekst przed wygenerowaniem kodu.

trans-unit.source: Use the ServiceContractGenerationContext object passed to the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IServiceContractGenerationExtension.GenerateContract%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method to modify the code document object model prior to the generation of code.
trans-unit.target: Użyj obiektu ServiceContractGenerationContext przekazany do <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IServiceContractGenerationExtension.GenerateContract%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metodę, aby zmodyfikować kod document object model przed generowanie kodu.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IServiceContractGenerationExtension.GenerateContract%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Typically, the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IServiceContractGenerationExtension?displayProperty=fullName> interface is implemented on a custom <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension?displayProperty=fullName> implementation that is used to import custom WSDL elements or otherwise modify the code at the service or operation level.
trans-unit.target: Zazwyczaj <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IServiceContractGenerationExtension?displayProperty=fullName>interfejs jest wdrażany na niestandardowego <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension?displayProperty=fullName>wdrożenia, który służy do importowania elementów WSDL niestandardowych lub zmodyfikować kod na poziomie usługi lub operacji, w przeciwnym razie wartość.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IServiceContractGenerationExtension?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: To modify the code at the operation level, see <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IOperationContractGenerationExtension?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Aby zmodyfikować kod na poziomie operacji, zobacz <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IOperationContractGenerationExtension?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IOperationContractGenerationExtension?displayProperty=fullName>
